videos.description: Kyle Bambard 43 yd FG MISSED
videos.headline: NC State field goal hits the post

videos.description: Deshaun Watson pass complete to Wayne Gallman for 18 yds Wayne Gallman fumbled, forced by Dravious Wright, recovered by NCSt Airius Moore
videos.headline: Wayne Gallman leaves game with injury after fumble

videos.description: Clemson RB Wayne Gallman is hit hard, resulting in him fumbling the ball, which would be recovered by NC State. Gallman would need assistance from trainers leaving the game.
videos.headline: Clemson RB Gallman leaves game after taking big hit

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson RB Gallman leaves game after taking big hit) 2016/10/15 ESHEET

videos.description: NC State QB Ryan Finley's pass is tipped and falls into the arms of Clemson's K'Von Wallace for the interception.
videos.headline: Clemson comes down with INT off tipped pass

videos.description: NC State's goal line defense prevails on fourth down after denying Clemson QB Deshaun Watson a touchdown, resulting in the Wolfpack getting the ball back.
videos.headline: NC State denies Clemson at goal line on fourth down

videos.description: NC State WR Kelvin Harmon comes down with a great sideline catch which gains 24 yards and leads to a Wolfpack field goal.
videos.headline: NC State WR Harmon makes tremendous catch on sideline

videos.description: Kyle Bambard 28 yd FG GOOD
videos.headline: NC State ties the game with field goal

videos.description: Deshaun Watson makes a big-time throw to Ray-Ray McCloud for a 16-yard first down.
videos.headline: Clemson converts on fourth-and-long

videos.description: Clemson QB Deshaun Watson's pass is completed to Mike Williams for a 13-yard touchdown, the first of the game for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Watson finds Williams for first TD of game

videos.description: Deshaun Watson's pass is intercepted for a touchdown by NC State's Mike Stevens to even the score at 10.
videos.headline: Watson throws pick-six on first play of 2nd half

videos.description: At the two-yard line, Clemson RB Tyshon Dye attempts to force his way into the end zone, but instead loses the ball and the fumble is recovered by NC State.
videos.headline: Clemson's goal line struggles continue

videos.description: Deshaun Watson's pass is intercepted for a touchdown by NC State's Mike Stevens to even the score at 10.
videos.headline: Watson throws pick-six on first play of 2nd half

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Watson throws pick-six on first play of 2nd half) 2016/10/15

videos.description: Deshaun Watson pass complete to Mike Williams for 17 yds Mike Williams fumbled, forced by Niles Clark, recovered by NCSt Shawn Boone  , return for 66 yds to the Clem 26
videos.headline: Clemson fumbles again near the end zone

videos.description: NC State's Kyle Bambard's 37-yard field goal attempt is blocked by Clemson's Christian Wilkins to keep the game tied at 10.
videos.headline: Clemson blocks NC State's go-ahead field goal attempt

videos.description: Clemson WR Mike Williams catches the ball for a first down, only to have it stripped by NC State, resulting in the Tigers' fourth giveaway of the day.
videos.headline: Clemson commits fourth turnover of game

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Clemson commits fourth turnover of game) 2016/10/15 ESHEET

videos.description: Clemson QB Deshaun Watson breaks through the arms of an NC State defender and runs four yards into the end zone to give the Tigers the lead back.
videos.headline: Watson gets into the end zone for first rushing TD of season

videos.description: NC State RB Matthew Dayes rushes up the middle through Clemson's defensive line into the end zone to tie up the score at 17.
videos.headline: NC State ties game up with 2-yard TD run

videos.description: Deshaun Watson pass incomplete to Hunter Renfrow
videos.headline: Hunter Renfrow injured on incompletion

videos.description: NC State's kicker Kyle Bambard misses his third field goal of the game, this one an attempt to win the game, to keep the game knotted up at 17 against Clemson.
videos.headline: NC State misses potential game-winning field goal

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (NC State misses potential game-winning field goal) 2016/10/15

videos.description: Clemson QB Deshaun Watson throws to Artavis Scott in the end zone for a 10-yard touchdown to give the Tigers the lead in overtime over NC State.
videos.headline: Clemson takes lead in OT with Watson's 10-yard TD pass

videos.description: Ryan Finley's pass is intercepted in the end zone by Clemson's Marcus Edmond to lock up the Tigers' 24-17 overtime victory over NC State.
videos.headline: Interception in OT seals win for Clemson

videos.description: NC State's Kyle Bambard misses a game-winning field goal at the end of regulation, sending the game to overtime. In the extra session, Deshaun Watson tosses a 10-yard touchdown and the Tigers make an interception on the next drive, preserving a 24-17 win.
videos.headline: Clemson survives scare from NC State, wins in OT

videos.description: The Tigers beat the Wolfpack 24-17 in overtime but needed a 1-for-4 kicking performance by NC State to stay in the game. With a visit to a Florida State looming, No. 3 Clemson has offensive adjustments to make.
videos.headline: Clemson's narrow win raises red flags

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Analysis (Planning for Success: Clemson) 2016/10/15 ODV
